# 📧 InboxArmor — Email Spam Detector

InboxArmor is a fast and lightweight web app that detects whether an email is spam or not using a trained SVM machine learning model. It’s built with Flask and offers a clean UI with mobile-friendly design.

## 🚀 Features

- 💡 ML-powered (SVM) spam classification
- 📊 90%+ accuracy with TF-IDF vectorization
- 🌗 Light/Dark mode toggle
- 🕒 Local email history
- 📱 Responsive design

## 🌐 Live Demo

👉 [Try InboxArmor](https://emailspamdetector-jggl.onrender.com)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JS  
- **Backend**: Python, Flask  
- **ML**: scikit-learn (SVM)
